comments: Bogdanovic (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Caruso (LAL).
Correctly called 24 second violation.  Additionally, the shot clock violation occurs prior to any illegal contact from Bagley III (SAC) to James (LAL).
Bagley III (SAC) is already in James' (LAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
McGee (LAL) makes body to body contact with Fox (SAC) that affects his shot near the rim.
Rondo (LAL) is already in Bogdanovic's (SAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Bogdanovic (SAC) makes marginal contact with Kuzma (LAL) as he defends the shot attempt.
Kuzma (LAL) makes incidental contact with Bagley III (SAC) during rebounding.
Barnes (SAC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends James' (LAL) drive to the basket.
Barnes (SAC) legally contests James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
James (LAL) is already in Fox's (SAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Bogdanovic (SAC) legally contests Kuzma's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) clamps James' (LAL) arm and affects his ability to secure the rebound.
Bagley III (SAC) is already in Caruso's (LAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Barnes (SAC) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Barnes (SAC) and Rondo (LAL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
Bogdanovic (SAC) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
McGee (LAL) wraps Bagley III (SAC) with two arms during the inbound.
Kuzma (LAL) places his hand momentarily on Hield's (SAC) side before immediately correcting.
Barnes (SAC) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
[Observable in enhanced video] Hield (SAC) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Kuzma (LAL).
Kuzma (LAL) legally contests Hield's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
